#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga "
msgstr "1. Immersion "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Dutiyakulaputtasutta "
msgstr "4. A Gentleman (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.416, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.4:1.1"
msgid "“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajitā yathābhūtaṃ abhisamesuṃ, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisamesuṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, whatever gentlemen—past, "

msgctxt "sn56.4:1.2"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajitā yathābhūtaṃ abhisamessanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisamessanti. "
msgstr "future, "

msgctxt "sn56.4:1.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajitā yathābhūtaṃ abhisamenti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisamenti. "
msgstr "or present—truly comprehend after rightly going forth from the lay life to homelessness, all of them truly comprehend the four noble truths. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.4:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.4:2.2"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ. "
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. … "

msgctxt "sn56.4:2.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajitā yathābhūtaṃ abhisamesuṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.4:2.4"
msgid "abhisamessanti … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.4:2.5"
msgid "abhisamenti, sabbe te imāni cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisamenti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.4:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.4:3.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
